# Try to find the OpenEXR libraries
# This check defines:
#
#  OPENEXR_FOUND - system has OpenEXR
#  OPENEXR_INCLUDE_DIR - OpenEXR include directory
#  OPENEXR_LIBRARIES - Libraries needed to use OpenEXR
#
